Events in the year '''2017 in [[Liechtenstein]]'''.
==Incumbents== * [[Prince of Liechtenstein|Prince]]: [[Hans-Adam II, Prince of Liechtenstein|Hans-Adam II]] * [[Prince of Liechtenstein|Regent]]: [[Alois, Hereditary Prince of Liechtenstein|Alois]] * [[List of heads of government of Liechtenstein|Prime Minister]]: [[Adrian Hasler]]
==Events== *5 February &ndash; [[Liechtenstein general election, 2017]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.volksblatt.li/nachricht.aspx?p1=fl&id=122035&src=vb|title=Landtagswahlen 2017: Rekordzahl an Kandidaten |work=Volksblatt |language=German |accessdate=5 February 2017}}</ref>
===Sport=== * The [[2016–17 Liechtenstein Cup]] is the 72nd season of [[Liechtenstein]]'s annual cup competition. The first round, second round and quarterfinals took place in 2016. The semifinals are scheduled to be held on 5 and 11 April 2017, and the final on 24 May.<ref>{{Cite web |title = FL1 Aktiv-Cup 2016/17 |url = http://www.lfv.li/nationalewettbewerbe/fl1-aktiv-cup/spielplan-20162017/ |website = lfv.li |accessdate = 5 February 2017 |language = German |deadurl = yes |archivedate= 2017-03-27 |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170327081234/http://www.lfv.li/nationalewettbewerbe/fl1-aktiv-cup/spielplan-20162017/ }}</ref> The cup winner qualifies to the [[2017–18 UEFA Europa League#First qualifying round|first qualifying round]] of the [[2017–18 UEFA Europa League]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kassiesa.net/uefafiles/2017-18-uefa-access-list.pdf |title=Access list for the 2017/18 UEFA club competitions |website=kassiesa.net ||accessdate=5 February 2017}}</ref> In the final, on 24 May 2017, [[FC Vaduz]] won 5:1 over [[USV Eschen/Mauren]].<ref>{{Cite web |title = FL1 Aktiv-Cup 2016/17 |url = http://www.lfv.li/nationalewettbewerbe/fl1-aktiv-cup/spielplan-20162017/ |website = lfv.li |accessdate = 22 September 2018 |language = German |deadurl = yes |archivedate= 2017-06-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170623203230/http://www.lfv.li/nationalewettbewerbe/fl1-aktiv-cup/spielplan-20162017/ }}</ref>
