of Daegu]]. The current bishop is Constantine Bae Ki Hyen, appointed in 2016.
==History== On February 15, 1966 [[Pope Paul VI]] established the Diocese of Masan with territory taken from the [[Roman Catholic Diocese of Busan|Diocese of Busan]].<ref name=hierarchy>{{cite web|url=http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/dmasa.html|title=Diocese of Masan|publisher=Catholic-Hierarchy|accessdate=2014-02-13}}</ref><ref name=GCatholic>{{cite web|url=http://www.gcatholic.org/dioceses/diocese/masa1.htm|title=Diocese of Masan 마산|publisher=Giga Catholic|accessdate=2014-02-13}}</ref>
